PN,36201
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1784819906
OL,3,CManchester synagogue terrorist's phone
OL,4,Cnot examined when arrested before
OL,5,Cattack
OL,7,FA police chief constable has said he
OL,8,Fis "deeply sorry" after admitting
OL,9,Fphones of a terrorist were seized
OL,10,Fmonths before he carried out an attack
OL,11,Fat a synagogue - but never examined to
OL,12,Funcover his "extremist mindset".
OL,14,FJihad Al-Shamie, 35, was shot dead by
OL,15,Fpolice on 2 October 2025 while he
OL,16,Fcarried out the attack at the Heaton
OL,17,FPark Hebrew Congregation synagogue in
OL,18,FCrumpsall, Manchester in which two
OL,19,Fworshippers were killed.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/15
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,363,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1784819906
OL,3,CManchester synagogue terrorist's phone
OL,4,Cnot examined when arrested before
OL,5,Cattack
OL,7,FHis phones, containing details of his
OL,8,Fextremist mindset and terror-fixation,
OL,9,Fhad been seized by Greater Manchester
OL,10,FPolice but officers did not analyse
OL,11,Fthe contents until after he launched
OL,12,Fthe attack.
OL,14,FNow Chief Constable of the force, Sir
OL,15,FStephen Watson, has apologised after
OL,16,Fadmitted there was a "missed
OL,17,Fopportunity" to potentially uncover
OL,18,Fthe plot.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/15
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,363,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1784819906
OL,3,CManchester synagogue terrorist's phone
OL,4,Cnot examined when arrested before
OL,5,Cattack
OL,7,FThe apology came after Al-Shamie's
OL,8,Ffriend and accomplice, Mohammad
OL,9,FBashir, 31, was sentenced to life
OL,10,Fimprisonment with a minimum term of 17
OL,11,Fyears for planning a separate terror
OL,12,Fattack with Al-Shamie on the UK
OL,13,FDefence Academy at Shrivenham.
OL,15,FFollowing the 2 October attack,
OL,16,FWhatsApp messages and voice note
OL,17,Fexchanges between the pair were
OL,18,Funcovered when police analysed two
OL,19,Fphones seized from Al-Shamie when when
OL,20,Fhe was arrested twice prior to the
OL,21,Fattack, Manchester Crown Court heard.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/15
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,363,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1784819906
OL,3,CManchester synagogue terrorist's phone
OL,4,Cnot examined when arrested before
OL,5,Cattack
OL,7,FHe was detained in February 2025 over
OL,8,Fan alleged breach of a non-molestation
OL,9,Forder and in September 2025 when he
OL,10,Fwas held on suspicion of rape
OL,12,FAfter the hearing, Sir Stephen said:
OL,13,F"The conclusion of legal proceedings
OL,14,Fagainst Bashir means that the rules
OL,15,Fwhich prevent the sharing of
OL,16,Finformation about live criminal cases
OL,17,Fare now lifted.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/15
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,363,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1784819906
OL,3,CManchester synagogue terrorist's phone
OL,4,Cnot examined when arrested before
OL,5,Cattack
OL,7,F"Today therefore marks the first
OL,8,Fpossible opportunity for me to provide
OL,9,Fadditional information as to the
OL,10,Fnature of the contact that GMP had
OL,11,Fwith Al-Shamie prior to his cowardly
OL,12,Fattack upon those attending the
OL,13,Fsynagogue.
OL,15,F"It is factually the case that Al-
OL,16,FShamie had come to the notice of GMP
OL,17,Fin respect of two linked criminal
OL,18,Fallegations which did not relate to
OL,19,Fterrorist offences.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/15
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,363,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1784819906
OL,3,CManchester synagogue terrorist's phone
OL,4,Cnot examined when arrested before
OL,5,Cattack
OL,7,F"These allegations resulted in his
OL,8,Fbeing arrested on the 13th February
OL,9,F2025 on suspicion of breaching a non-
OL,10,Fmolestation order; and on the 21st
OL,11,FSeptember 2025 on suspicion of rape.
OL,13,F"At the time of his committing the
OL,14,Fattack at the Heaton Park Synagogue,
OL,15,FAl-Shamie was on police bail.
OL,17,F"In conducting an internal review, it
OL,18,Fbecame apparent that GMP had seized Al-
OL,19,FShamie's mobile devices, at the point
OL,20,Fof each arrest.
OL,26,@yD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/15
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,363,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1784819906
OL,3,CManchester synagogue terrorist's phone
OL,4,Cnot examined when arrested before
OL,5,Cattack
OL,7,F"The significance of the data contents
OL,8,Fof these devices was substantial in
OL,9,Frespect of evidencing an extremist
OL,10,Fmindset.
OL,12,F"Regrettably, I can confirm that the
OL,13,Fsignificance of the information stored
OL,14,Fon Al-Shamie's devices was not
OL,15,Frealised as they had not been examined
OL,16,Fbefore the attack took place on the
OL,17,F2nd of October 2025.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/15
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,363,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1784819906
OL,3,CManchester synagogue terrorist's phone
OL,4,Cnot examined when arrested before
OL,5,Cattack
OL,7,F"There can however, be little doubt
OL,8,Fthat the information contained within
OL,9,Fthese devices would have inspired
OL,10,Ffurther investigative action.
OL,12,F"It is clear that our not having
OL,13,Freviewed the data available to us
OL,14,Fprior to the attack constitutes a
OL,15,Fmissed opportunity.
OL,17,F"It is clear that our not having
OL,18,Freviewed the data available to us
OL,19,Fprior to the attack constitutes a
OL,20,Fmissed opportunity.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/15
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,363,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36209
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1784819906
OL,3,CManchester synagogue terrorist's phone
OL,4,Cnot examined when arrested before
OL,5,Cattack
OL,7,F"I am disappointed at the prospect of
OL,8,Fadding to the distress of all of those
OL,9,Faffected by the terrible events last
OL,10,FOctober.
OL,12,F"For this, I am deeply sorry.
OL,14,F"It is my fervent hope and expectation
OL,15,Fthat the continuing independent
OL,16,Freviews and processes will be able to
OL,17,Fdraw together all the available
OL,18,Fevidence such as to leave no question
OL,19,Funanswered.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/15
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,363,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36210
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1784819906
OL,3,CManchester synagogue terrorist's phone
OL,4,Cnot examined when arrested before
OL,5,Cattack
OL,7,F"I have already made direct contact
OL,8,Fwith those personally affected by Al-
OL,9,FShamie's barbarism, together with
OL,10,Frepresentatives of our Jewish
OL,11,Fcommunity, to apprise them of this
OL,12,Fdevelopment.
OL,14,F"I thank them for their continuing
OL,15,Fsupport.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/15
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
