PN,36211
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1784819906
OL,3,CManchester synagogue terrorist's phone
OL,4,Cnot examined when arrested before
OL,5,Cattack
OL,7,F"GMP is unwavering in our commitment
OL,8,Fto all people across Greater
OL,9,FManchester and to strive to do all
OL,10,Fthat is possible to sustain the fight
OL,11,Fagainst hatred, extremism and
OL,12,Fterrorism."
OL,14,FSir Stephen said the forthcoming
OL,15,Finquests into the deaths of the two
OL,16,Fmen murdered by Al-Shamie at the
OL,17,Fsynagogue, Melvin Cravitz and Adrian
OL,18,FDaulby, will examine "all aspects of
OL,19,Fthe attack" and the Independent Office
OL,20,Ffor Police Conduct (IOPC) is also
OL,21,Fconducting a review.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/15
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
