PN,36212
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1784819906
OL,3,CManchester synagogue terrorist's phone
OL,4,Cnot examined when arrested before
OL,5,Cattack
OL,7,FHe said it is for the IOPC and the
OL,8,Fcoroner to determine the "impact" of
OL,9,Fpolice not reviewing the contents of
OL,10,FAl-Shamie's devices before the attack
OL,11,Ftook place.
OL,13,FThe IOPC said they are investigating
OL,14,Fall previous contact between GMP and
OL,15,FAl-Shamie, including action taken by
OL,16,Fpolice n response to reports of crimes
OL,17,Fcommitted by him.
OL,26,@pD@ZOUpD@aO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G12/15
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,363,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36213
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1784819906
OL,3,CManchester synagogue terrorist's phone
OL,4,Cnot examined when arrested before
OL,5,Cattack
OL,7,FA spokesman said: "As part of our
OL,8,Finvestigation, we will consider
OL,9,Fwhether GMP missed any opportunities
OL,10,Fto prevent the tragic events that
OL,11,Foccurred last year.
OL,13,F"Last week, GMP made us aware of
OL,14,Finformation relevant to these
OL,15,Finquiries which was recovered from
OL,16,Fdevices seized as part of its
OL,17,Finvestigations into Al-Shamie's
OL,18,Falleged offending.
OL,20,F"We will review this evidence as part
OL,21,Fof our ongoing investigation.
OL,26,@oD@SOUuD@AOU|D@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G13/15
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
