SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1784819906
OL,3,CManchester synagogue terrorist's phone
OL,4,Cnot examined when arrested before
OL,5,Cattack
OL,7,F"We have advised one officer that they
OL,8,Fare under investigation for potential
OL,9,Fmisconduct in relation to their
OL,10,Fhandling of allegations of rape and
OL,11,Fother sexual offences against Al-
OL,12,FShamie.
OL,14,F"This does not necessarily mean that
OL,15,Fdisciplinary proceedings will follow.
OL,16,FThis decision will be made on
OL,17,Fconclusion of the investigation."
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@AOUyD@aO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G14/15
